/K%E1%BB%B3-6/poem-zj0ojo7VNPsd4cI28vFS9w">Kỳ 6 - 其六</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-H%C3%A0m/author-FUm0aTv6MMEhKSvKSGMoVA">Vũ Phạm Hàm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/M%E1%BA%A1c-Thi%C3%AAn-T%C3%ADch/L%E1%BB%99c-tr%C4%A9-th%C3%B4n-c%C6%B0/poem-9ri-UMcCSrG1WoclefaI6g">Lộc trĩ thôn cư - 鹿峙村居</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/M%E1%BA%A1c-Thi%C3%AAn-T%C3%ADch/author-GLzqIGvVnoBURna-hgD_jw">Mạc Thiên Tích</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%E1%BB%81n-%C4%90%E1%BB%97/Nga-My-s%C6%A1n-nguy%E1%BB%87t/poem-ukMH4UJV1LL3HdR_XO88DQ">Nga My sơn nguyệt - 峨眉山月</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%E1%BB%81n-%C4%90%E1%BB%97/author-qvR5jQ1KJBBzJ7wiP-fcNA">Tiền Đỗ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Loan/Th%E1%BB%A9-B%E1%BA%AFc-C%E1%BB%91-s%C6%A1n-h%E1%BA%A1/poem-h2uSLzv46nsnzy7Emq6rxw">Thứ Bắc Cố sơn hạ - 次北固山下</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Loan/author-gHhaiQ8ke0xPqu10oTgjow">Vương Loan</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%C3%B4-%C4%90oan-Ti%E1%BA%BFt-Ph%C3%BAc-di%C3%AAn-gi%E1%BA%A3n-Ti%E1%BA%BFt-Hoa-tu%C3%BD-ca/poem-BwIUN62ITz7qjguBHWccGg">Tô Đoan, Tiết Phúc diên giản Tiết Hoa tuý ca - 蘇端、薛復筵簡薛華醉歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
